    <h1>ABOUT</h1>
    <p>Hive Solutions began in 2008, when two former <b>Microsoft</b> employees got together to make a different kind of technology from what the market was providing. After half a year of initial Research & Development, the project grew with collaborators from companies such as <b>Deloitte</b> and <b>Wipro</b>.</p>
    <p>We have gathered experience both in the development and customization of large-scale management information systems, believing, from the start, that the available market options used outdated paradigms and technologies, thereby missing all the new opportunities leveraged by available modern methodologies.</p>
    <p>It was also our belief that consulting processes were too expensive and complex, and could benefit from a more pragmatic and objective approach.</p>
    <p>These ideas make up <b>Hive Solutions</b>, a new kind of consultancy: agile, results-oriented and deeply technical.</p>
